    "description": "Are you a skilled Real Estate Agent looking for your next big career move? Sunteck Realty Asia Pacific Associates in Aurangabad offers you the perfect platform to grow professionally and personally.\n\nAbout Sunteck Realty Asia Pacific Associates:\nSunteck Realty Asia Pacific Associates is a leading organization in the Remote sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Maintain a pipeline of qualified leads using CRM software\n• Coordinate with legal teams for documentation and title verification\n• Negotiate pricing, terms, and conditions on behalf of clients\n• Build relationships with channel partners and brokers\n• Prepare presentations and proposals for institutional clients\n• Conduct site visits and property presentations for clients\n• Achieve monthly and quarterly sales targets\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• MBBS / MD / MS from recognized medical college\n• 1-3 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Due Diligence\n• Proficiency in AutoCAD\n• Proficiency in RERA Compliance\n• Proficiency in GIS Tools\n• Proficiency in Client Relationship Management\n• Proficiency in Property Valuation\n• Proficiency in Property Management\n• Proficiency in Real Estate Law\n\nWork Mode: Remote - Work from anywhere in India\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• International travel opportunities for senior roles\n• Competitive salary with performance-linked incentives\n• Maternity and paternity leave\n• Recognition and rewards programs\n• Modern office with recreational facilities\n• Learning & development budget\n• Salary Range: 4 LPA - 9 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Aurangabad, Maharashtra, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Sunteck Realty Asia Pacific Associates!",
